he y1d1d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">People.&quot; </div><div class="t m1384 x5b he y1d1d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"> </div><div class="t m602 x4e h44 y198a ff4 fs18 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON M.—October 19, 1895. </div><div class="t m1685 x55 h2f y17fc ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">THE GENUINE PRINCIPLE OF LIBERTY. </div><div class="t m1ac3 x64 h2f y1ed1 ff4 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">I. FOR </div><div class="t ma9e x12 he y1ed1 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">what kind of rights and liberty may even selfish men </div><div class="t m9f5 x26 he y1864 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">plead? Ans.—Their </div><div class="t m767 x69 h21 y1864 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">own </div><div class="t m6f3 x47 he y1864 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rights and their </div><div class="t m767 x70 h21 y1864 ff6 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">own </div><div class="t ma6e xa5 he y1864 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">liberty. </div><div class="t m1f3 x61 he y1eea ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m218 xc he y1eea ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What kind of liberty did the Lord command the children </div><div class="t mf2 x26 he y1d26 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of Israel to proclaim at the year of jubilee? Ans.—Universal </div><div class="t m8cc x26 he y14de ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">liberty. Lev. 25 : to. (See note 1.) </div><div class="t m104a x61 he y1da9 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m9c1 xc5 he y64c ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How did He rebuke them for not heeding this instruction? </div><div class="t m442 x26 he y64d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jer. 34: 17. </div><div class="t mb7 x61 he yb5f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m11e xc he y16a5 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">For whom had they not proclaimed liberty? Same verse. </div><div class="t m2a0 x26 he y20af ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(See note 2.) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
